{"tid":2152041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果頭條: 警撿慈善基金文件涉受訪者 《蘋果》申禁令保新聞材料","createTime":"2020-08-11T17:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T18:10:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4236d7d8d40eb096bde135d142e217001f3660dc","tid":2152041,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/117642912_10159347468442448_2182498156608064431_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=g14VtCPk9cUAX-fgPr0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=7&amp;oh=63f93ffb2351a0357e1ab686c5f5f470&amp;oe=5F59E9A2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F117642912_10159347468442448_2182498156608064431_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3Dg14VtCPk9cUAX-fgPr0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D7%26oh%3D63f93ffb2351a0357e1ab686c5f5f470%26oe%3D5F59E9A2&h=96d67ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方前日動員200警力大肆搜查將軍澳蘋果日報大樓，並撿取大批證物，包括《蘋果日報》慈善基金多份文件及主機硬碟等。《蘋果》總編輯羅偉光表示，警方撿取的慈善基金資料中涉及新聞材料，《蘋果》決定申請臨時禁制令，以保護資料不被警方查閱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10159347468437448/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fphotos%2Fa.170516952447%2F10159347468437448%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=d530c354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/photos/a.170516952447/10159347468437448/</a>"},{"pid":"dcf9365a0a157a4d9a68d388e0426c073f5d49fc","tid":2152041,"uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:29:44.000Z","msg":"聽日可能又要行好多間先搵到蘋果買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0bfb5a5839e837178792f53d783830667d03e7","tid":2152041,"uid":169529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T17:30:37.000Z","m